verbose_text: The water / fat in-phase condition was chosen to maximize SNR and to eliminate water / fat dependent signal phase offsets.30 While eXpresso (thick black lines, N SPP> 1) only allows for a very limited number of imaging shot durations, the imaging shot duration in Ristretto can be chosen on a fine grid (gray lines).
